      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un starp Rekabeama\nNammu un starp Jerobeama\nNammu bija Karfch wiſſâ Laikâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Rekabeams aismigge\nar faaweem Tehweem/ un tappe\npee faaweem Tehweem Dahwida\nPilli aprakts. Un winna Mahte-\ntes Wahrdâ bija Naëma/ weena\nAmmoniterene/ un winna Dehls\nAbijams tappe par Kehnizu win-\nna Weeta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XV. Nodalla.\nAbijams weens besdeewigs : 1. Un pehz winna\nAfus winna Dehls/weens deewabihjigs Keh-\nnisch pahr Juhdu/ walda weens pehz ohtru\nJerusaleme : 9. Afus schihsta to Semmi\nno teem Elka-Deeweem : Karro muhscham\nprett Baësu : 19. Nomirst / un Josawats\ntohp par Kehnizu winna Weetâ : 24. Ma-\ndabs Kehninsch eekſch Israëla tohp no Ba-\nesus nokants : 25./28. Kas arri par Kehni-\nnu tappę pahr Israëln / un isdelde Jero-\nbeama Namnu : 29.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "U N astotapadefinitâ\nGaddâ ta Kehnizu Je-\nrobeama Neebata Deh-\nla/ ktua Abijams par Kehnizu\npahr Juhdu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Trihs Gaddus waldija\nwinch Jerusalemê / un winna\nMahtei bija Maëka Wahrdâ/\nAbisaloma Meita.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas staigaja wiſſês fa-\nwa Tehwa Grehekês / ko tas\npreeksch winnu bija darrijs / un\nwinna Sirds ne bija gohdigt ar\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "to KUNGU fawn Deewu / ka\nwinna Tehwa Dahwida Sirds.\nBet Dahwida deht dewe\ntas KUNGS winna Deews\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "weenu Gaifchunu Jerusaleme\nceezeldams winna Dehlu pel-\nwinnu un Jerusalemi stiprina-\ndams/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz ka Dahwids da-\nrijs/ kas pareiſt bija preeksch t-\nKUNGA Azzim/ un ne btj a-\nlahpis no wiſſa/ ko winſch tai-\nbij pawehleje/ wiſſâ winna Dsi-\nwibas Laikâ/ bes ween eekſch u-\nrtiſa ta Getiteza Leetas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet starp Rekabeama u-\nJerobeama Nammu bija Karſch-\nkamehr tas dſihwoja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kas wehl atleek no V-\nbijama/ un wiſſ/ ko tas irr da-\nrijs/ tas irr rakstihts to Kehniz-\nno Juhda Laiku-Grahmata. u-\nKarſch bija starp Abijannu u-\nstarp Jerobeainit.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Abijams aismigge a-\nfaaweem Tehweem/ un tee aprak-\nwinnu Dahwida Pilli/ un win-\nna Dehls Affus tappę par Keh-\nnizu winna Weetâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un diwidefinitâ Gadd-\nJerobeama ta Israëta Kehnizu-\ntappę Affus par Kehnizu pahr\nJuhdu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un waldija tschetrdefinit\nun weenu Gaddu Jerusalemê\nUn winna Mahtei bija Maë-\nWahrdâ Abisaloma Metta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Affus darrija / ka-\ntam KUNGAM labbi patikke-\nittinka winna Tehws Dahwids\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo winsch tsdsinne toh-\nMauzineekus no tahs Senmes-\nun atnehrie wiſſus Elka - Dee-\nwuſko winna Tehws bij darrijs\n"
    }
  ],
